Floors of Fantasy is a top-down-view co-op puzzle game where the player takes control of Green and Red and tries to navigate through stages filled with tricky puzzles. Each stage has 3 floors, with each floor being progressively harder than the previous one.

There are 5 stages in total, each with 3 rooms. Later stages include a special mechanic present for puzzle solving.

This game can be played in a single-player mode and in multiplayer locally.

[DEFAULT CONTROLS] (PC)
Player 1 > W, A, S, D
Player 2 > Up, Left, Down, Right
Pause Game > [TAB]

